name: Alan Partridge - Textual Inversion V1
description:
This is a textual inversion trained on pictures of the character Alan Partridge, played by Actor Steve Coogan.

First time creating a TI based on a male object.

Done as requested by @silkpurse. I hope it's somewhat what you wanted ;)

Not quite sure how it turned out, please let me.

Please make sure to emphasize that the subject is (male), otherwise it tends to render females.

Still learning and improving the progress of the training, any feedback is welcome.

Feel free to leave me a tip/buy me a coffee if you like what I am doing :)
